                        "type": "stat_block_section",
                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "Two Actions"
                    },
                    "effect": "You cause the  *wraithweave patch* and the object it contains to become incorporeal. This effect lasts as long as you Sustain the activation. The  *wraithweave patch* can only be touched, held, and carried by an incorporeal creature, and returns to solid form if not carried by such a creature\u2014if the  *wraithweave patch* is in a solid object at this time, it tears apart and the item inside is either lost forever or simply lodged within the solid object, at the GM's discretion.",
                    "requirement": "the wraithweave patch has been wrapped around an object and you are incorporeal",
                    "activation_types": [
                        {
